{"tid":1959317,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★Rich逃不了！美富商湧入度假勝地　致當地確診暴增成","createTime":"2020-04-05T10:11:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-05T12:16:26.000Z","uid":19454,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"57a2d8a398fde846e5fdf8db3b2fe56575dc26d8","tid":1959317,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T10:11:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/20200405/323518946202488832.jpeg/mnIl-WIv-eVViY0W--7etHd6D032m3FJkKK7-JCiu_g?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F20200405%2F323518946202488832.jpeg%2FmnIl-WIv-eVViY0W--7etHd6D032m3FJkKK7-JCiu_g%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=516f6b5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n隨着富人逃離城市湧入度假勝地，當地官員稱，新冠病例數目不成比例地上升，相當氣憤，擔心當地小型醫院會不堪負荷。<br />\n<br />\n距離愛達荷州滑雪勝地太陽谷（Sunny Valley）最近的克川市（Ketchum）市長布拉德肖（Neil Bradshaw）警告，當地不是「病毒假期」之地。<br />\n<br />\n去年滑雪季時，太陽谷總計有42.65萬名滑雪遊客到訪。數十年來，該處一直是億萬富翁和名流愛去的旅遊熱點，包括荷里活巨星阿諾舒華辛力加、Facebook行政總裁朱克伯格和70年代荷里活性感女星瑪麗蓮夢露等。截至2日，太陽谷所在的布萊恩縣（Blaine County）已有351宗確診案例，但全縣只有2.2萬人居住。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E8%AA%AA/457046/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E7%BE%8E%E5%AF%8C%E5%95%86%E6%B9%A7%E5%85%A5%E5%BA%A6%E5%81%87%E5%8B%9D%E5%9C%B0-%E8%87%B4%E7%95%B6%E5%9C%B0%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA%E6%9A%B4%E5%A2%9E%E6%88%90-%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%E7%86%B1%E9%BB%9E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E4%25B8%2596%25E7%2595%258C%25E8%25AA%25AA%2F457046%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%25AF%258C%25E5%2595%2586%25E6%25B9%25A7%25E5%2585%25A5%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E5%2581%2587%25E5%258B%259D%25E5%259C%25B0-%25E8%2587%25B4%25E7%2595%25B6%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25A8%25BA%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%25A2%259E%25E6%2588%2590-%25E7%2597%2585%25E6%25AF%2592%25E7%2586%25B1%25E9%25BB%259E&d=4DrNtUYtvprXc3sGeUgfzyMX%2BuEjOoKUanh%2Bi4Xf2cM%3D&h=3473ba89\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E8%AA%AA/457046/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E7%BE%8E%E5%AF%8C%E5%95%86%E6%B9%A7%E5%85%A5%E5%BA%A6%E5%81%87%E5%8B%9D%E5%9C%B0-%E8%87%B4%E7%95%B6%E5%9C%B0%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA%E6%9A%B4%E5%A2%9E%E6%88%90-%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%E7%86%B1%E9%BB%9E</a><br />\n<br />\n布拉德肖在《愛達荷山快報》（Idaho Mountain Express）專欄指出，「我們必須勸阻朋友和遊客前來。對於一個曾經相當歡迎遊客的小鎮來說，這很難做到，但我們必須減少遊客人數」。"},{"pid":"558a660be8e95cd9466d578ab5923ccd737a23c6","tid":1959317,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T10:12:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2662f6676bd6220d3ca4eac4bb5d60c771ebcaff","tid":1959317,"uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T10:13:02.000Z","msg":"貧者一萬留一千，富者一萬留二三，<br />\n貧富若不回心轉，看看死期在眼前。<br />\n平地無有五穀種，謹防四野絕人煙，<br />\n若問瘟疫何時現，但看九冬十月期。"},{"pid":"4ddbd2d22798580ec9090054a0544483ac524483","tid":1959317,"uid":53062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T10:15:57.000Z","msg":"唔驚，有錢人可以買呼吸機"},{"pid":"2fcd8470bc357c05e737bc12677abf144a161c66","tid":1959317,"uid":161374,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4ddbd2d22798580ec9090054a0544483ac524483","tid":1959317,"uid":53062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T10:15:57.000Z","msg":"唔驚，有錢人可以買呼吸機"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T10:17:42.000Z","msg":"首先有錢人係唔會中，獨立屋，有車，唔反工<br />\n買定一年糧食就搞掂"},{"pid":"f3ff5b51ef9ab212fdf0e6704d12fd40ad2d9038","tid":1959317,"uid":268591,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T10:18:34.000Z","msg":"香港還有9唔9說真話的勁人<br />\n香港人應該出黎撐袁國勇，對抗共狗<br />\n有冇用都要